{"tid":9432,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d人咁鍾意約埋一齊去放狗?","createTime":"2016-11-28T15:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T06:01:21.000Z","uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4458795e86dca7e9e4267d75880f09427f42a219","tid":9432,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"我本身自己都有養狗<br />\n之前成日都同一個狗主好好緣份<br />\n我地差唔多日日放狗都見到面<br />\n之後佢就成日都好似想同我一齊放狗咁<br />\n又傾下自己隻狗放完又會一齊走<br />\n其實我都唔係好想佢跟埋黎一齊放<br />\n因為原本想靜靜地自己放狗<br />\n同享受下同狗狗慢慢咁散步既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後放完就返屋企<br />\n如果佢係到既話又要同佢講野<br />\n之後結果係企係到傾計仲多過散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來我怕左佢<br />\n我決定避開佢放狗既時間同地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一日好耐冇見又見返佢<br />\n之後見到佢身邊有3、4個狗友一齊行<br />\n個時心諗點解要一齊行姐<br />\n放完狗就好返屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e819d10db40f3ea91b3011a7a93823ab723bfef","tid":9432,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"狗有狗扑<br />\n人有人扑"},{"pid":"07f23c36cd6e987db82972098e59002323eb6781","tid":9432,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗有狗扑<br />\n人有人扑</blockquote><br />\n我同佢同兩隻狗全部都係女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f595c2bfb01f548205e40c02bbb233c35e26e89","tid":9432,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"我發現都幾多養狗既人係咁 <br />\n特別係如果你地養同一品種既狗<br />\n會好熱情好多野講<br />\n我呢啲毒撚好多時都只係想佢快啲收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa863f3a368fd067b967f301aacefe9e8fa41f0f","tid":9432,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"有幾咁奇<br />\n我都會約埋一齊去金魚街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e3f9e217d4b027230ab54343046a14f5a2700a","tid":9432,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狗有狗扑<br />\n人有人扑</blockquote><br />\n我同佢同兩隻狗全部都係女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想一齊整豆漿"},{"pid":"0ef18c4f144b29ee16c50c628331a0c2881c0385","tid":9432,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發現都幾多養狗既人係咁 <br />\n特別係如果你地養同一品種既狗<br />\n會好熱情好多野講<br />\n我呢啲毒撚好多時都只係想佢快啲收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個d通常都係約埋出去行山丶狗公園多<br />\n個d我又覺得冇咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係落樓下都要一齊放就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n+1 我都係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}